Guvf vf Gnfx 01 bs gur Rhqlcghyn Punyyratr
------------------------------------------

Jevgr n Yvahk xreary zbqhyr, naq fgnaq-nybar Znxrsvyr, gung jura ybnqrq
cevagf gb gur xreary qroht ybt yriry, "Uryyb Jbeyq!"  Or fher gb znxr
gur zbqhyr haybnqnoyr nf jryy.

Gur Znxrsvyr fubhyq ohvyq gur xreary zbqhyr ntnvafg gur fbhepr sbe gur
pheeragyl ehaavat xreary, be, hfr na raivebazrag inevnoyr gb fcrpvsl
jung xreary gerr gb ohvyq vg ntnvafg.

Cyrnfr fubj cebbs bs guvf zbqhyr orvat ohvyg, naq ehaavat, va lbhe
xreary.  Jung guvf cebbs vf vf hc gb lbh.  V'z fher lbh pna pbzr hc jvgu
fbzrguvat.  Nyfb or fher gb fraq gur xreary zbqhyr lbh jebgr, nybat jvgu
gur Znxrsvyr lbh perngrq gb ohvyq gur zbqhyr.

Erzrzore gb hfr lbhe VQ nffvtarq va gur Fhowrpg: yvar jura erfcbaqvat gb
guvf gnfx, fb gung V pna svther bhg jub gb nggevohgr vg gb.  Lbh pna
whfg erfcbaq gb gur gnfx jvgu gur nafjref naq nyy fubhyq or svar.
